WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
NEW JERSEY TO BERMUDA.
DNC 16, DNC 17.
1. 41 FOOT S/V, WHITE HULL WITH BLUE STRIPE,
   ONE PERSON ON BOARD, UNREPORTED JERSEY CITY
   (40-20.00N 073-45.00W) AT 050447Z NOV TO
   BERMUDA (32-21.75N 064-49.0W).
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A
   SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO US COAST GUARD LANTAREA,
   PHONE: 757 398 6700, E-MAIL: LANTWATCH@USCG.MIL.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2532/23, 2550/23.
